been Naruto's strong suit.

53
00:06:49,574 --> 00:06:51,514
-Well, that's why
Kakashi-sensei is

54
00:06:51,524 --> 00:06:53,634
having him learn the technique
through action, right?

55
00:06:53,644 --> 00:06:54,614
-Yeah.

56
00:06:54,614 --> 00:06:57,584
Training only Naruto can do.

57
00:06:57,594 --> 00:06:59,524
They can double the
amount of training

58
00:06:59,534 --> 00:07:05,584
he gets by using two
clones, and he's using 200.

59
00:07:05,584 --> 00:07:09,584
-Still, incorporating a change
in chakra nature into a jutsu

60
00:07:09,594 --> 00:07:13,584
by itself is a difficult
enough hurdle to get over.

61
00:07:13,584 --> 00:07:16,534
To say nothing of the fact
that the Rasengan was a jutsu

62
00:07:16,544 --> 00:07:18,544
